ch.usz.c3pro.c3_pro_android_framework

Class C3PRO

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.usz.c3pro.c3_pro_android_framework.C3PRO

  • public class C3PRO
extends java.lang.Object
    * This class will provide the FHIR Context and, if you initialize it with a FHIR Server URL, a dataqueue as a singleton. For the data to outlive activity lifecycles, it should be initialized in your application onCreate. The FHIR Context is a costly object and you should only keep one instance around.
